#, fuzzy
msgid "Through the https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-micrometer-registry/[Quarkiverse Micrometer registries]"
msgstr "A través de los link:https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-micrometer-registry/[registros del Micrómetro Quarkiverse]"

#: _posts/2025-11-14-micrometer-prometheus-v1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Via OpenTelemetry, using a bridge provided by the https://quarkus.io/guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry[Micrometer and OpenTelemetry] extension. This setup allows Micrometer metrics to be sent as OpenTelemetry metrics, offering a unified output via the https://opentelemetry.io/docs/specs/otlp/[OpenTelemetry OTLP protocol]."
msgstr "A través de OpenTelemetry, utilizando un puente proporcionado por la extensión link:https://quarkus.io/guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry[Micrometer y OpenTelemetry] . Esta configuración permite que las métricas de Micrometer se envíen como métricas de OpenTelemetry, ofreciendo una salida unificada a través del link:https://opentelemetry.io/docs/specs/otlp/[protocolo OTLP de OpenTelemetry] ."

#: _posts/2025-11-14-micrometer-prometheus-v1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For more details on Observability in Quarkus please visit https://quarkus.io/guides/observability[this guide]."
msgstr "Para más detalles sobre la observabilidad en Quarkus, visite link:https://quarkus.io/guides/observability[esta guía] ."

